  "story": {
    "beat": "The trail plunges into a humid, ancient jungle that swallows sound. The trees are older than the village; something watches from the canopy.",
    "narration": [
      "The air grows heavy, smelling of damp earth and sweet, rotten orchids.",
      "Illinois Jim pauses. The birds have stopped singing. The canopy is listening.",
      "To go forward, we must climb. The ancient ruins lay somewhere beneath the roots."
    ]
  },
